JDK - It stands for Java development kit. To install java we need to install JDK. It is a software
developing environment used to developing java applications. JDK includes the JRE which stands for
Java runtime environment which get all the requirements to run the applications.

Using JDK and JRE we create java program then with help of javac we compiled the java program
after that with help of java we execute the compiled java program.

JVM (Java virtual machine) where java program runs.
JRE present inside JDK.